Skryba bundles and builds on third-party open-source software.

================================================================================
whisper.cpp
================================================================================
High-performance inference of OpenAI's Whisper model in C/C++.
Copyright (c) 2023-2025 The ggml authors (Georgi Gerganov and contributors).
Licensed under the MIT License.
https://github.com/ggml-org/whisper.cpp

Skryba vendors a prebuilt `whisper.xcframework` (v1.9.1, macOS slice) under
Frameworks/. It provides the Metal-accelerated transcription engine.

================================================================================
Whisper models (ggml format)
================================================================================
The speech-recognition models are downloaded on demand from:
https://huggingface.co/ggml-org/whisper.cpp

The underlying Whisper model is by OpenAI, released under the MIT License.
Models are not redistributed with this repository; the app fetches them at
runtime to the user's Application Support directory.
